results.name: Decimal expansion of sqrt(2730).
comment: Continued fraction expansion of sqrt(2730) is 52 followed by (repeat 4, 104).
xref: Cf. A002193 (decimal expansion of sqrt(2)), A002194 (decimal expansion of sqrt(3)), A002163 (decimal expansion of sqrt(5)), A010465 (decimal expansion of sqrt(7)), A010470 (decimal expansion of sqrt(13)), A177924 (decimal expansion of (28+sqrt(2730))/56).
